-- Obama to make "fiscal cliff" statement at 1:30 P.M. ET
-- 
-- Mon Dec 31, 2012 1:02pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/12/31/us-usa-fiscal-obama-statement-idUSBRE8BU0AR20121231

 

 WASHINGTON  (Reuters) - President Barack Obama will make a statement at 1:30 p.m. EST on Monday at an event with "middle class Americans," the White House said. 
 (Reporting by  Jeff Mason  and  Roberta Rampton )